ext_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01070">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, [3.?] 9. 1900</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
